The template variable <strong>$PriceDynamic</strong> displays the price of a variation including the surcharge. When using this variable, the item price is updated automatically depending on the selected variation. <br>
<strong>Display as additional costs</strong> = VAT will not be taken into account for the entered surcharge. One possible use for this option is to set up a bottle deposit which is added to the item price without calculating VAT. Properties that have this option selected will be displayed as separate items on invoices etc. These items will be displayed with the <strong>ID -2</strong>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
