<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Activate to make the property available in the order process. Depending on the <strong>property type</strong>, the customer can e.g. enter a text or value or select an option from a drop-down menu. The design of order properties can be adjusted in the CSS. Go to <strong>CMS » Web design » Layout » CSS » CSSOrder</strong> and save your own CSS code for the order process.</p></td>
</tr>
