<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Property links for markets and price comparison portals</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the market property from the drop-down menu or activate the property link for a market. For further information about creating properties for markets and price comparison portals, refer to the markets' pages in the topic <a href="/en/omni-channel/multi-channel">Multi-Channel</a>.</p></td>
</tr>
