<h2 id="760">9. Setting up labels</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Item labels are attached to an item or to the item packaging. Labels can contain information about the price, contents, etc. Define the size as well as the position of all item parameters and order parameters you wish to print on the label.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Creating a label template:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » Item » Labels</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Expand the <strong>New template</strong> area.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as desired. Pay attention to the information given in table 14.</p>
</li>
<li>
