</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Print test page</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Depending on which printer you use, the printed labels may differ from the template settings even if all settings are correct. Therefore, we recommend printing a few test pages while setting up the template. Print some test pages on normal paper before using label paper. Adjust the positions until you have reached the desired result.</p>
