<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-tip" title="Tip"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Displaying new <strong>Default</strong> items in the item overview</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The new <strong>Default</strong> item is still inactive. In order to display recently created items in the item overview in the <strong>Item » Edit item</strong> menu, select the <strong>ALL</strong> option for the <strong>Active</strong> filter in the search area and click on <strong>Search</strong>. Learn how to activate your items and variations for the online store in the <a href="/en/item/managing-items#180">Setting the availability</a> chapter.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
