<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The variation number is assigned automatically based on the pattern saved in the <strong>System » Item » Settings</strong> menu. Variation numbers can be changed subsequently in the <strong>settings</strong> tab of a variation.</p></td>
