<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter the external variation ID for the main variation of the item. The external variation number is optional. It facilitates importing items and variations from external systems to plentymarkets. External variation IDs can be changed subsequently in the <strong>Settings</strong> tab of a variation.</p></td>
</tr>
