<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="50">14.4. Entering item texts</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter your item texts in the <strong>Texts</strong> tab. Along with the preview text, which is displayed in the online store’s item list, you can also enter a description as well as additional texts, e.g. technical data and keywords.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Entering item texts:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Item » Edit item</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the item.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>Texts</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the language.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the item texts. Pay attention to the information given in table 18.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
