<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Technical data</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter the item’s technical data. To display the technical data in the online store, insert the template variable <strong>$TechnicalData</strong> and, if needed, a title into the template <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/cms-syntax#web-design-itemview-container-itemviewsingleitem">ItemViewSingleItem</a>.</p></td>
