<div class="sect3">
<h4 id="200">17.1.2. Displaying the availability in the online store</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>By default, the availability is displayed in the online store using the <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/cms-syntax#web-design-itemview-container-itemviewsingleitem">ItemViewSingleItem</a> template. Use the template variables <strong>$AvailabilityString</strong> and <strong>$AvailabilityIcon</strong> to display the availability text and icon in the online store. By default, these template variables are included in the template <strong>ItemViewSingleItem</strong> of the plentymarkets default design.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock important">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-important" title="Important"></i>
</td>
