<div class="title">Availability is not displayed correctly in the online store</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you use your own store icons for the availability, upload files for all availability options. Otherwise, an empty frame will be displayed in the design when the icon is missing.<br>
If the availability is not displayed correctly in the online store after changes were made, then delete the browser cache and reload the page.</p>
</div>
</td>
