<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="290">17.7. Specifying shipping data</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In addition to global shipping information which you activate in the <strong>Global</strong> tab, you specify further data, such as warehouses and surcharges, in the <strong>Shipping</strong> area of the variation.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Specifying the shipping data of the main variation:</p>
</div>
