<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="312">17.10. Adding warehouses for the variation</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In the <strong>Warehouse</strong> tab of a variation, you select warehouses for the product and enter warehouse information, i.e. reorder level and maximum stock. For further information, refer to the <a href="/en/stock-management">Stock</a> page of the manual.</p>
