<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Setting</th>
<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Explanation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Storage location type</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select a storage location type based on the size of the variation.</p></td>
