</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Reorder level</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter a value. If the stock reaches or falls below this value, a reorder is created. If stock is reserved, then even positive stock can reach or fall below the reorder level. Variations below the reorder level can be filtered in the menu <a href="/en/stock-management/managing-stocks">Stock » Stocks</a>. The minimum reorder quantity is displayed in the <strong>RL Delta</strong> column.</p></td>
</tr>
