<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Stock buffer</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter a value for the stock buffer. The stock for particular markets will then be reduced by this value.<br>
