Values entered are valid for the markets <a href="/en/omni-channel/multi-channel/neckermann-at">Neckermann.at</a>, <a href="/en/omni-channel/multi-channel/otto">OTTO</a>, <a href="/en/omni-channel/multi-channel/rakuten">Rakuten</a>, <a href="/en/omni-channel/multi-channel/plus-gartenxxl">Plus.de</a>. The buffer entered here takes priority over the buffer values entered for the particular market.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Suggested storage location</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the storage location for the warehouse or select <strong>Default storage location</strong>. The storage location is suggested automatically when reordering. Select <strong>Default storage location</strong> if no storage location should be assigned.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Labels</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Click on <strong>Labels</strong> to generate labels for the warehouse based on a template. For further information, refer to the <a href="/en/item/managing-items#760">Setting up labels</a> chapter.</p></td>
</tr>
