<div class="paragraph">
<p>Edit multiple variations with the <strong>Variation group function</strong> or the <strong>Batch processing</strong> function in the <strong>Item</strong> menu. The group function edits previously selected variations. The batch processing function edits previously filtered variations.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Carrying out the variation group function:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Item » Edit item</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>In the search, select <strong>Variations</strong> in the <strong>Table type</strong> drop-down menu.</p>
</li>
<li>
