<p>Go to <strong>Item » Edit item</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the <strong>filters</strong>. Pay attention to the information given in table 35.<br>
→ The <strong>Active</strong> filter is set to <strong>Yes</strong> by default.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Search</strong>.<br>
→ All items found will be displayed in the overview.</p>
</li>
</ol>
