<div class="paragraph">
<p>In addition to the default index, you use the extended index to activate parameters that are taken into account when performing an item search with the <strong>Browse description</strong> option in the search area of the <strong>Item » Edit item</strong> menu. Set up the extended index in the same way.</p>
