<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="2020">23.3. Editing Set items</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Now that you have created the <strong>Set</strong> item, you can refine the settings for the set.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Editing Set items:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Item » Edit item</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the <strong>Set</strong> item.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as desired. Pay attention to the information given in table 39.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
