<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Add tags for the item. Learn how to use tags in the <a href="/en/item/managing-items#150">Adding tags to items</a> chapter.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Revenue account</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter the revenue account. For further information about the revenue account, refer to the <a href="/en/order-processing/orders/_accounting#90">Accounting</a> page of the manual.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
