<div class="paragraph">
<p>Serial numbers can also be used in the plentymarkets Client. In order for serial numbers to be available for use in the plentymarkets Client, the <strong>Serial number</strong> option must have been activated in the item’s <strong>Global</strong> tab.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Activating the serial number function:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Item » Edit item</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the item that has serial numbers that you want to use.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>Global</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the setting <strong>Yes</strong> for the option <strong>Serial number</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The plentymarkets Client allows you to <a href="/en/basics/automation/processes/procedures#420">automate the registration of serial numbers</a>.</p>
